thread.title: Music streaming service Deezer to raise up to 406 mln eur in IPO
thread.title_full: Music streaming service Deezer to raise up to 406 mln eur in IPO | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Music streaming service Deezer to raise up to 406 mln eur in IPO
text:
PARIS Oct 15 Music streaming service Deezer said it expects to raise between 300 million and 406 million euros ($345-$466 million) from selling new shares when it lists on the Paris stock exchange later this month.
The company set a price target for the initial public offering of between 36.40 euros and 49.24 euros, and plans to sell 8.242 million new shares. Deezer said an over-allotment option meant that could increase by up to 15 percent.
Deezer said in a statement on Thursday that the price of the shares would be set on Oct. 27, with trading on Euronext Paris due to start on Oct. 30. ($1 = 0.8705 euros) (Reporting by James Regan ; Editing by Ingrid Melander )
